OL,3,CPrice of Guernsey milk to go up by 4%
OL,4,Cdue to increased costs
OL,6,FThe wholesale price of Guernsey milk
OL,7,Fwill rise by 4% from Monday 1 July,
OL,8,Fthe island's dairy has announced.
OL,10,FIt is due to a range of factors
OL,11,Fincluding the upkeep of the ageing
OL,12,Fdairy, a volatile supply chain and
OL,13,Ffarmers needing a higher markup to
OL,14,Foffset the drop in direct government
OL,15,Fsupport.
OL,17,FMark Thompson, Guernsey Dairy
OL,18,FManagement Board Chairman, explains:
OL,19,F"The baseline funding which the
OL,20,Findustry receives has significantly
OL,21,Freduced and
