OL,3,CPrice of Guernsey milk to go up by 4%
OL,4,Cdue to increased costs
OL,6,Fcontinues to be eroded each year by
OL,7,Fthe impact of inflation.
OL,9,F"The result is farmers are having to
OL,10,Frely more on income from the milk the
OL,11,FGuernsey Dairy purchases, and that is
OL,12,Fhaving to be passed on to consumers
OL,13,Fthrough the retail price."
OL,15,FRetailers can choose whether to absorb
OL,16,Fsome or all of the higher wholesale
OL,17,Fcost for milk or pass it on to
OL,18,Fcustomers.
