OL,6,FGuernsey Dairy is forecasted to make a
OL,7,Ftrading loss of around #200,000 in
OL,8,F2024 with the island's Environment and
OL,9,FInfrastructure Committee reviewing
OL,10,Flocal dairy farming to try and find a
OL,11,Fsustainable, long-term plan for the
OL,12,Findustry.
OL,14,FIts proposals are expected to be
OL,15,Fdebated by the States later this year.
